On the street of Mangaung -  Modern vintage— it’s a mixture of high street clothing and retro clothing. If you love dressing up and wanting to add a bit of charm into your style, modern retro fashion is definitely something you’d want to try out. Always remember that when it comes to modern retro fashion, you need to mix the right amount of classics or “oldies” and modern basics and trends. Too much vintage could make you look like a young granny